overview: Two brothers think they have found a golden investment formula. By having a computer trade automatically, they want to take their emotions out of the equation to make money from other peopleâ€™s emotion-driven investments. Their trust has more than a million Euros in hand, but disappointing results push them ever further towards a situation where they can no longer pay the rent of their canal-side apartment in Amsterdam. To keep afloat, they have to put out all the stops - and most of all control their emotions.
title: Up or Out
